    {
      "title": "PRICE_FILTER",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "price_filter",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "`/exchangeInfo format:`"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "json",
          "json": {
            "filterType": "PRICE_FILTER",
            "minPrice": "0.00000100",
            "maxPrice": "100000.00000000",
            "tickSize": "0.00000100"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The `PRICE_FILTER` defines the `price` rules for a symbol. There are 3 parts:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`minPrice` defines the minimum `price`/`stopPrice` allowed; disabled on `minPrice` == 0.",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`maxPrice` defines the maximum `price`/`stopPrice` allowed; disabled on `maxPrice` == 0.",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`tickSize` defines the intervals that a `price`/`stopPrice` can be increased/decreased by; disabled on `tickSize` == 0.",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Any of the above variables can be set to 0, which disables that rule in the `price filter`. In order to pass the `price filter`, the following must be true for `price`/`stopPrice` of the enabled rules:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`price` >= `minPrice`",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`price` <= `maxPrice`",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "(`price`-`minPrice`) % `tickSize` == 0",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "LOT_SIZE",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "lot_size",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "`/exchangeInfo format:`"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "json",
          "json": {
            "filterType": "LOT_SIZE",
            "minQty": "0.00100000",
            "maxQty": "100000.00000000",
            "stepSize": "0.00100000"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The `LOT_SIZE` filter defines the `quantity` (aka \"lots\" in auction terms) rules for a symbol. There are 3 parts:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`minQty` defines the minimum `quantity` allowed.",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`maxQty` defines the maximum `quantity` allowed.",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`stepSize` defines the intervals that a `quantity` can be increased/decreased by.",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "In order to pass the `lot size`, the following must be true for `quantity`:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`quantity` >= `minQty`",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`quantity` <= `maxQty`",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "(`quantity`-`minQty`) % `stepSize` == 0",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "MARKET_LOT_SIZE",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "market_lot_size",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "`/exchangeInfo format:`"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "json",
          "json": {
            "filterType": "MARKET_LOT_SIZE",
            "minQty": "0.00100000",
            "maxQty": "100000.00000000",
            "stepSize": "0.00100000"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The `MARKET_LOT_SIZE` filter defines the `quantity` (aka \"lots\" in auction terms) rules for `MARKET` orders on a symbol. There are 3 parts:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`minQty` defines the minimum `quantity` allowed.",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`maxQty` defines the maximum `quantity` allowed.",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`stepSize` defines the intervals that a `quantity` can be increased/decreased by.",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "In order to pass the `market lot size`, the following must be true for `quantity`:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "`quantity` >= `minQty`",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "`quantity` <= `maxQty`",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "(`quantity`-`minQty`) % `stepSize` == 0",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "MAX_NUM_ORDERS",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "max_num_orders",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "`/exchangeInfo format:`"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "json",
          "json": {
            "filterType": "MAX_NUM_ORDERS",
            "limit": 200
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The `MAX_NUM_ORDERS` filter defines the maximum number of orders an account is allowed to have open on a symbol."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Note that both \"algo\" orders and normal orders are counted for this filter."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "MAX_NUM_ALGO_ORDERS",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "max_num_algo_orders",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "`/exchangeInfo format:`"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "json",
          "json": {
            "filterType": "MAX_NUM_ALGO_ORDERS",
            "limit": 100
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The `MAX_NUM_ALGO_ORDERS` filter defines the maximum number of all kinds of algo orders an account is allowed to have open on a symbol."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The algo orders include `STOP`, `STOP_MARKET`, `TAKE_PROFIT`, `TAKE_PROFIT_MARKET`, and `TRAILING_STOP_MARKET` orders."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "PERCENT_PRICE",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "percent_price",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "`/exchangeInfo format:`"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "json",
          "json": {
            "filterType": "PERCENT_PRICE",
            "multiplierUp": "1.1500",
            "multiplierDown": "0.8500",
            "multiplierDecimal": 4
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The `PERCENT_PRICE` filter defines valid range for a price based on the mark price."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "In order to pass the `percent price`, the following must be true for `price`:"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "ordered": false,
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "BUY: `price` <= `markPrice` * `multiplierUp`",
              "blocks": []
            },
            {
              "text": "SELL: `price` >= `markPrice` * `multiplierDown`",
              "blocks": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "MIN_NOTIONAL",
      "level": 3,
      "id": "min_notional",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "blockquote",
          "text": "`/exchangeInfo format:`"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "json",
          "json": {
            "filterType": "MIN_NOTIONAL",
            "notional": "5.0"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "The `MIN_NOTIONAL` filter defines the minimum notional value allowed for an order on a symbol. An order's notional value is the `price` * `quantity`. Since `MARKET` orders have no price, the mark price is used."
        }
      ]
    }
